posting_body: ['Welcome Home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHE/NJQK', 'Whether you take advantage of the many different activities the lake has to offer, or just enjoy the quiet solitude of the sinking sun casting colors across the water, living "on the lake" at Gleason Lake Apartments is truly a Minnesota experience.', 'Our residents enjoy our outdoor spaces, including our private dock, club room, and 24-hour fitness center.', 'Some of our newly renovated apartments feature in-unit laundry, hardwood floors, and newly updated kitchens.', 'Underground parking is available.', 'Fiber-optic internet service is available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Gleason Lake Apartments home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Air conditioning', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Patio or balcony options', 'Washer and dryer - in select homes', 'Storage space', 'Ceiling fan', 'Walk-in closet', 'Community Amenities', 'Private dock', 'Party room', 'Fitness center', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Package receiving', 'Elevator access', 'Gleason Lake Apartments Information', 'Address:', '155 Gleason Lake Rd, Wayzata MN, 55391', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=2', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Deposit:', '$300 - 600 (Note: Varies By Number Of Cats ($100-$200 Non-Refundable))', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '8:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '11:00AM - 3:00PM', 'Sunday:', 'Closed']
